1 지수분포

n = 10000
u = runif(n, 0,1)
x1 = -log(1-u)
x2 = - log(u)
df = data.frame(x1=x1, x2=x2)
summary(df)

\(x \sim Exp(1)\)일 때, \(y = x/\lambda \sim Exp(\lambda)~(\lambda > 0)\)가 된다. \(\lambda\)는 rate 모수로 \(E(y) = 1/\lambda\)이다.

lambda = 5
y = x1/lambda
summary(y)
##      Min.   1st Qu.    Median      Mean   3rd Qu.      Max. 
## 0.0000471 0.0567655 0.1385308 0.2025537 0.2789008 1.8759253
hist(y)

3 삼각분포

rtri1은 삼각분포 확률변수 1개를 생성하는 함수이고, rtri는 \(n\)개의 삼각분포 확률변수를 생성하는 함수이다.

rtri1 = function() {
  accept=FALSE
  while(accept==FALSE) {
    x = runif(1, 0, 2)
    u = runif(1, 0, 1)
    accept_prob = ifelse(x <= 1, x, 2-x)
    if( u <= accept_prob) {
      accept = TRUE
    }
  }
  return(x)
}
rtri1()
## [1] 0.4078156
rtri = function(n) {
  x = numeric(n)
  for(i in 1:n) x[i] = rtri1()
  
  return(x)
}
n = 1000
x = rtri(n) 
summary(x)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
## 0.09935 0.71174 0.99301 1.00311 1.30919 1.98448
hist(x)

data.frame(x=x) %>% ggplot(aes(x=x)) + geom_histogram()
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

data.frame(x=x) %>% ggplot(aes(x=x)) + geom_density()

3.1 정규 확률변수

rnor1 = function() {
  M = 2/sqrt(exp(1))
  accept=FALSE
  while(accept==FALSE) {
    x = rcauchy(1, 0, 1)
    u = runif(1, 0, 1)
    accept_prob = (1+x^2)*exp(-x^2/2)/M
    if( u <= accept_prob) {
      accept = TRUE
    }
  }
  return(x)
}
rnor1()
## [1] 1.446114
rnor = function(n) {
  x = numeric(n)
  for(i in 1:n) x[i] = rnor1()
  
  return(x)
}
n = 1000
x = rnor(n) 
summary(x)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
## -2.9775 -0.6142  0.0324  0.0363  0.6873  3.6485
hist(x)

data.frame(x=x) %>% ggplot(aes(x=x)) + geom_histogram()
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

data.frame(x=x) %>% ggplot(aes(x=x)) + geom_density()
